    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Most readers found that Arthur Lubow's profile of Rem Koolhaas showed the architect to be cold and overintellectual, both personally and in his designs. Readers were split about Walter Kirn's take on summer jobs -- some waxed nostalgic, while others wanted to take him out behind the woodshed.</p>
